{"header":{"word":"קִרְיׇה","entry":8717,"letter":"ק","strongs":7151,"page":900},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" &#134; [[קִרְיׇה]] ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"n.f.","body":" town, city (syn. of [[עִיר]], chiefly poet., and in the higher style; perhaps from above &#8730; as meeting-place of men; cf. n.pr.loc. MI:13 [[קרית]], l.:10 [[קריתן]]; JAram. [[קַרְיׇה]]);&#8212;abs. &#180;[[ק]]: Is 1:21 +; cstr. [[קִרְיַת]] Nu 21:28 +;&#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"1.","body":" in gen. De 2:36 De 3:4. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"2.","body":" of specif. towns, Ho 6:8 ([[גִּלְעָד]], LXX:Codd. <span class=\"greek\">Galgala</span>, cf. Now); [[קִרְיַת סִיחׂן]] Nu 21:28; Damascus, [[מְשׂוֹשִׂי]] &#180;[[ק]]: Je 49:25 (&#8214;[[עִיר תְּהִלָּה ]]); esp. of Jerus. Mic 4:10, Is 29:1, Is 33:20, &#180;[[רְחׂבוֹת ק]]: La 2:11, [[מֶלֶךְ רָָב]] &#180;[[ק]]: Ps 48:3, city for inhab. 1Ki 1:41, 1Ki 1:45, &#180;[[ק]]: [[נֶאֱמָנׇה]] Is 1:21, Is 1:26 (&#8214;[[עִיר הַצֶּדֶק ]]), [[עַלִּיזׇה]] &#180;[[ק]]: Is 22:2 (&#8214;[[עִיר ]] [[הוֹמִיָּה]]), Is 32:13. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"3.","body":" in Is 24-26 coll., i.e. denoting various, representative, cities, [[תּׂהוּ]] &#180;[[ק]]: Is 24:10, &#180;[[ק]]: [[בְּחוּרָה]] Is 25:2, [[גּוֹיִם עָרִיחִים]] &#180;[[ק]]: v:Is 25:3, [[נִשְׂגׇּבָה]] &#180;[[ק]]: Is 26:5; so prob. Hb Hab 2:8, Hab 2:17. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"4.","body":" indef., Hb Hab 2:12 (&#8214;[[עִיר ]]); Pr 29:8, [[עׂז]] &#180;[[ק]]: Pr 18:19 a city of strength, so [[עֻזּוֹ]] &#180;[[ק]]: Pr 10:15 (in fig.) = Pr 18:11 (id.); = inhab., Pr 11:10, &#180;[[הֲמוֹן ק]]: Job 39:7.\r","content":"definition","show":"block"}],"notes":"","etymology":[],"morphology":[]}